As Triceradon and Stegotron are heading towards the maximal base, they find
a stasis pod lying on the ground.  They open it and find out that their old
friend Ultracon is inside.  
Stegotron: Welcome back Ultracon! We thought you didn't make it.
Triceradon: Yeah.  And you  just missed all the fun. We got to fight some
predocon scum.
